           INSPECT  PK-THKJLR002   TALLYING
                    WORK-QUOTA-CNT FOR  ALL CONT-QUOTA
      *
           IF  WORK-QUOTA-CNT > ZERO
           THEN
                   MOVE  ZERO               TO  SQLCODE
